  "id": "did:web:etzhayyim.com:actor:mitooshi",
  "name": "mitooshi",
  "displayName": "見通し — Probabilistic Forecasting Observatory",
  "displayNameJa": "見通し",
  "displayNameEn": "Mitooshi",
  "description": "Probabilistic forecasting observatory — the charter-clean inverse of a quant trading bot. Emits probability distributions over PUBLIC time-series (chokepoint transit-load, congestion, availability, flow-rate, price-index, search-interest) routed to resilience/planning/early-warning (danjo/kanae/watari/watatsuna siblings), and NEVER places a trade, holds a position, or derives P&L (Charter §1.3 non-profit + yobel 'predictive market / derivative speculation' prohibition). The 'fact→error→weight→learn' loop is structural: a forecast carries its info-as-of stamp, the observation arrives later as an append-only datom, and the proper-scoring residual (CRPS/pinball/Brier/log-score) is the join across kotoba `as-of` — so a backtest can never see future data (look-ahead leak is structurally impossible on an append-only log). Residuals drive an EWMA bias + variance-inflation recalibration whose real training substrate is baien federated edge (Murakumo-only). Distribution-only (point-asserted=false, G1, 非終末論); non-speculative use (G2); primary-public sources only (G4); promotion only when the model beats a baseline AND is calibrated AND member-signed (G7/G9/G12).",
  "descriptionJa": "確率的予測の observatory — quant トレード bot の charter-clean な反転。公開時系列 (chokepoint transit-load / 混雑 / 可用性 / flow-rate / price-index / 検索関心) 上に確率分布を発行し、resilience/計画/早期警戒へ routing (danjo/kanae/watari/watatsuna 兄弟)、トレードも建玉も P&L も決して行わない (Charter §1.3 非営利 + yobel の predictive market/派生投機 禁止)。『事実→誤差→weight→学習』ループは構造的: forecast は info-as-of を刻み、観測は後から append-only datom で到着し、proper scoring residual (CRPS/pinball/Brier/log-score) は kotoba `as-of` 上の join → backtest が未来を見ることは不可能 (append-only log で先読みリーク構造的に不能)。residual が EWMA bias + 分散インフレ再較正を駆動、実訓練基盤は baien federated edge (Murakumo-only)。分布のみ (point-asserted=false, G1, 非終末論)、非投機用途 (G2)、一次公開ソースのみ (G4)、昇格は baseline 超え AND 較正済 AND member署名時のみ (G7/G9/G12)。",
  "adr": {
    "master": "etzhayyim:adr:2606051800",
    "watariSibling": "etzhayyim:adr:2606041827",
