    "r0": "etzhayyim:adr:2606051800",
    "r1": "reserved",
    "r2": "reserved"
  },
  "tier": "Tier-B",
  "scope": {
    "phase": "R0 — ontology + 6 lexicons + 5 cells (ALL 5 coded state machines: series_ingest/forecast_issue/backtest_score/online_update/calibration_gate; all .solve() RuntimeError at R0) + proper-scoring engine (methods/score.py — gaussian/quantile/categorical/ensemble) + backtest analyzer (methods/analyze.py — ALL 4 distribution kinds wired end-to-end with metric-appropriate baselines; emits scorecard + reliability diagram (PIT calibration) + derived datoms) + offline public-series normalizer (methods/ingest.py — G4 source membrane refuses proprietary terminals, G10 --live gated) + CROSS-ACTOR chokepoint bridge (methods/bridge.py — maps watari/watatsuna derived chokepoint aggregates into forecastable :series/:obs over the SHARED chokepoint keyword space; verified on the REAL watari/watatsuna outputs → 9 chokepoint series, malacca as both vessel-transit + cable-load) + END-TO-END LEARNING-LOOP integration test (test_learning_loop.py: biased model → its own residuals → CRPS 1.50→0.40, PIT 0.95→0.50 → promote) + MULTI-ROUND CONTINUAL-LEARNING test (test_continual_learning.py: EWMA correction converges to true bias AND re-converges on regime drift 2.0→4.0) + MULTI-HORIZON skill-decay analysis (methods/horizon.py: AR(1) φ=0.9, skill vs climatology +0.30 @h=1 → ≈0 @h=6 — honest useful-foresight range, 非終末論) + :representative seed (4 series / 4 models) + one-command runner (run_tests.sh). Registered in INFRA_ACTORS → did:web:etzhayyim.com:actor:mitooshi. 89 tests green (26 score + 24 cells + 9 analyze + 7 ingest + 6 bridge + 6 horizon + 6 learning-loop + 5 continual-learning). Design + datafication + offline scoring/recalibration only; NO live ingest/publish/promotion/training.",
    "scopeBoundary": "Probabilistic forecasting over public time-series + leak-free proper-scoring backtest + residual-driven recalibration (design-only)",
    "exclusions": [
      "trading / position-holding / P&L — unrepresentable (G2, N1)",
      "investment advice / rating / valuation / 業績予想 (G3, N2)",
