      "person-level prediction / pattern-of-life (N4)",
      "point-prophecy / deterministic final-state forecast (G1, N5, 非終末論)",
      "commercial-GPU training (G8, N6)",
      "server-signed model promotion (G9, N7)",
      "live data ingest / forecast publish / model promotion / federated backward pass (G10 — Council Lv6+ + operator)"
    ]
  },
